9. **Set Up Other Relevant Parts**: Initialize other non-ML components required by the application such as peripherals and communication modules.

This sketch should address all the issues encountered during the build process and provide a working implementation of your application. Make sure that the `model.h` file exists in the correct directory and contains the flatbuffer model data.

